text: Rental charges: Reasonable and Affordable price with comprehensive insurance cover with "0" access fee. Car return time can be delayed another 59 minutes with NO additional charges, that's a great chance to save money. Customer service so quick and car key can be collected in short period of time. BEST CAR RENTALS I HAVE EVER HAD
